told me the same thing in the past.

40:39.360 --> 40:40.520
I'm packing it in.

40:41.440 --> 40:43.720
I'll wait till my mum dies
'cause it would break her heart

40:43.800 --> 40:46.600
but when she goes, I'm packing it in.

40:51.400 --> 40:53.600
A woman, Roz,

40:55.360 --> 40:59.040
