you've done something wrong,

41:00.760 --> 41:02.240
"shame is everyone knowing."

41:04.760 --> 41:05.760
How right she was.

41:18.320 --> 41:20.000
Will you join me?

41:26.280 --> 41:27.360
I can't.

41:28.240 --> 41:29.280
Michael!

41:32.040 --> 41:33.080
I can't.

41:42.600 --> 41:44.960
This is Michael Kerrigan, Lord,
he's a good priest.

41:47.080 --> 41:50.840
He's quick to forgive others,
slow to forgive himself.

41:53.280 --> 41:54.600
Grant him peace, Lord.

41:56.280 --> 41:57.320
Amen.

42:01.680 --> 42:02.720
Thank you.

42:03.440 --> 42:04.440
(RAIN FALLING)

42:20.360 --> 42:21.360
Yeah?

42:21.440 --> 42:24.040
