42:25.920 --> 42:27.000
I nicked you once.

42:28.400 --> 42:29.680
I just wanted to have
a quick word with you,

42:29.760 --> 42:31.360
it's about Father Michael Kerrigan.

42:39.520 --> 42:41.520
MICHAEL'S MOTHER:
I'm sorry for how I treated you.

42:46.800 --> 42:47.920
I don't know what you mean.

42:50.240 --> 42:51.400
When you were young.

42:58.000 --> 42:59.480
I still don't know what you mean.

43:02.000 --> 43:03.280
I was a mess.

43:06.280 --> 43:07.760
Nerves on edge.

43:12.680 --> 43:13.720
Mum,

43:15.640 --> 43:17.040
