43:19.520 --> 43:20.920
That's all that I remember.

43:28.160 --> 43:30.080
Tell me something nice.

43:33.080 --> 43:34.120
Right.

43:36.960 --> 43:38.120
Remember Yaffee?

43:38.760 --> 43:40.080
He had that donkey?

43:42.640 --> 43:43.640
(CHUCKLES)

44:01.880 --> 44:02.920
Mum?

44:12.120 --> 44:14.160
(BREATHING HEAVILY)

44:20.400 --> 44:21.440
Oh, God,

44:22.160 --> 44:24.920
