to honour our father and mother,

44:26.520 --> 44:28.520
have compassion on my mother's soul.

44:29.360 --> 44:30.800
Forgive her her sins

44:31.760 --> 44:33.800
and grant that I may see her again

44:34.720 --> 44:37.000
in the joy of eternal brightness.

44:38.960 --> 44:40.280
Through Christ our Lord.

44:42.160 --> 44:43.160
Amen.

